		<h3>Learning Objectives</h3>
		<p>
		Compile a list of Learning Objectives that represent the goals of the presentation or course. What do you hope the students understand and retain? How do the students self-rate on their own grasp of the material? And which students are ahead and which ones are having a difficult time keeping up?
		</p><p>Metricalc gives you a variety of easy ways to discover and articulate your learning objectives in a form that is directly accessible by the particpants/
		</p>
