		<h3>Programs and Rounds</h3>
		<p>
		The basic building block is a Program. This could for example be a semester or a seminar or a lecture series. The same set of people participate over a span of time. They are the participants. During that time there might be classes, courses, presentations, visits or projects.
		</p><p>
		Metricalc periodically conducts a round of questions to all the students about their understanding or grasp of the material.
		</p>
